about what it's like on

01:25:12.270 --> 01:25:13.570
that other side of the line.

01:25:13.570 --> 01:25:14.870
I know I have [inaudible]
a lot today.

01:25:14.870 --> 01:25:16.170
And I hope that you
all did as well.

